From 885ba754feb790bab2fab32edd8ba33af8621389 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nandha Kishore Easwaran <nandhaki@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 4 Aug 2025 10:21:42 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 8/8] UPSTREAM: DP: Move rx ring allocation to arch specific
 file

1) Move rx ring allocation to arch specific code since refill
and monitor handling are changing in wifi8 arch.

2) Move reo ring setup and rx release ring setup into rx ring setup
to modularise it for different architectures.

Dependencies:
0450-0007-UPSTREAM-DP-Move-hash-routing-config-inside-arch-spe.patch

Signed-off-by: Nandha Kishore Easwaran <nandhaki@qti.qualcomm.com>
